<H2>Project overview</H2>The goal of the project was to provide =
techniques and=20
tools enabling a smart card issuer to verify that a new applet securely=20
interacts with already downloaded applets. A security policy has been =
defined=20
that associates levels to applet attributes and methods and defines =
authorized=20
flows between levels. We propose a technique based on mdeol checking to =
verify=20
that actual information flows between applets are authorized. The =
approach is=20
applied to a case study (an electronic purse running on Java enabled =
smart=20
cards). <A name=3Dpartic>
